{"tid":449111,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[要裝linux了] m$突擊清查企業有冇用老翻 大量中國公司中伏","createTime":"2017-10-27T01:49:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-27T04:22:07.000Z","uid":1886,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"8bd00473184fdf1912c466b7746c2cc1693ffaf3","tid":449111,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T01:49:44.000Z","msg":"微軟中國日前向上百家中國大陸公司發出律師函，要求各企業使用正版軟體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，並提供使用微軟系統的調查報告。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2017/10/24/98/4153949.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=1050&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2017%2F10%2F24%2F98%2F4153949.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D1050%26exp%3D3600&h=6303a1a1&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n微軟這次調查了旗下所有的軟體，尤其是辦公室應用軟體Word、Excel、PowerPoint、Visio等。目前已有上百家中國公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 收到了來自微軟的相關函件，其中多是上市公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n微軟此舉雖為捍衛正版軟體和智慧財產權制度，中國大陸企業可能會花錢改用正版，但也可能會轉向價格相對便宜的中國國產軟體。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/7333/2774988\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F7333%2F2774988&d=18JzV%2BojnVE0pgzis5M2DMmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=1f03ad27\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/7333/2774988</a>"},{"pid":"76547fa6fcf28104cea510d3def97f1afb32e051","tid":449111,"uid":77196,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T01:51:22.000Z","msg":"成堆鄰國狗個OS都係老翻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a79dc6550b3360f1610522e748d49e03f685a645","tid":449111,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T01:52:31.000Z","msg":"<bloc